column3: ICT prices based on current and historical basket definitions in terms of USD, PPP$ and as a % of monthly GNI per capita.

Historical medians for country groups were only calculated for the subset of economies with data available for all years. The number of countries included in a given calculation (for the world) is shown in the column "N (world)". Country groups were defined according to 2021 classifications (UN M49, World Bank income groups 2021, ITU BDT regions).
The definition of ICT price baskets has changed from time to time. This mapping table helps mapping historical price baskets to those currently used allowing a longer time series.
